          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each attack made by this unit or your STRIKE TEAM or BREACHER TEAM units within 24” and visible to this unit, a Hit Roll of 6 for that attack causes an additional hit. Each attack may only benefit from Devastating Unity once.</characteristic>
